<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:orientation="vertical"
    android:background="@drawable/home"
    tools:context="com.albaincompaniesltd.application.thetruemeaningofislam.org.albaincompaniesltd.application.thetruemeaningofislam.PillarsActivity">

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/txtjihad"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
        android:layout_gravity="center"
        android:layout_marginTop="50dp"
        android:text="What Makes a Good Muslim?"
        android:textColor="#fff"
        android:textSize="18sp"
        android:textStyle="bold" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView5"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginStart="77dp"
        android:layout_marginTop="150dp" />

    <ScrollView
        android:id="@+id/scroll1"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content">

        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/textView6"
            android:layout_width="320dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:textSize="16sp"
            android:padding="10dp"
            android:layout_gravity="center"
            android:text="A good Muslim is everything that the Prophet Muhamad P.B.U.H taught us to be- Modest, Humble, Truthful, Responsible, Just, Compassionate, Empathetic, Selfless as much as possible and to stay away from evil and corruption which is like what other religions teach.
To be a believer in Islam one has to be a good human being and incorporate all of the above mentioned qualities.\n\n

Respect is one of the key things a good Muslim should have. Respect falls under different categories: \n\n

* Respect for self

* Respect for your parents

* Respect for others

* Respect for the environment

It is also a requirement for a good Muslim to follow the pillars of Islam and pillars of faith.






"
            android:textColor="#fff"
            android:maxLines="10"
            android:minLines="1"
            android:ellipsize="end"
            android:scrollbars="vertical"
            />



    </ScrollView>


    <Button
        android:id="@+id/btnGoodMuslimNext"
        android:layout_width="300dp"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginLeft="40dp"
        android:background="#EA8B0F"
        android:gravity="center"
        android:text="Next Lesson"
        android:textColor="#fff" />

    <Button
        android:id="@+id/btnListenGoodMuslim"
        android:layout_width="300dp"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginLeft="40dp"
        android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
        android:background="#EA8B0F"
        android:gravity="center"
        android:text="Listen to Lesson"
        android:textColor="#fff" />


</LinearLayout>
